Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Motivation"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Motivation"\NWhat's wrong, Yuuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally lacking motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NWe're high schoolers now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.55,0:00:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a brand new semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.18,0:00:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find plenty of motivation\Nif you just stick to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even get motivated to find motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed\Nto get motivated to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motivation to find motivation, hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've just gotta do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be nice being a complete idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shinonome Lab"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shinonome Lab"\NHakase! Isn't it about time you woke up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My Ordinary Life 1"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:00:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's breakfast is grilled fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.65,0:01:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But I want {\i1}omurice{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just had some yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish is very nutritious, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.45,0:01:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have a balanced diet,\Nyou'll never grow--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.88,0:01:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um! That's supposed to be our breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I-It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This isn't a robotic part or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.22,0:01:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.23,0:01:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that cat need it more than we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I realized just this very moment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think I might have fallen in love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}24 hours a day of you you you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't get you out of my head!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something (something) feels different now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With you (together) it's awkward conversation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it (mutual love) no it's one-sided love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Uh-oh I think our eyes just met!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:03:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this anxious nervous feeling?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My train of thought is tangled with confusion...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This kind of thing is a first for me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be a fever and I'm sick?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With a sudden twist it's awakened love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's a fire in my cheeks and my face is all red{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Th-Th-This can't be real, my hands are trembling{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this what people mean when they talk about "love"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I-I'm stuttering non-stop talking to you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Awkward silence and then mumble-mumble-mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanna (I wanna) know how you feel about me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}O-O-O-One one-sided love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}O-O-O-One one-sided love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sparkle-sparkle dazzling I DO fall in love!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's like I'm flying through the sky{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}O-O-O-One one-sided love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Wooden doll" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Red cow" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Salmon" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio! {\i1}Selamat pagi{\i0}!\N[Malay for "Good Morning."]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yuuko. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?\NI forgot to put on my student badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did she just ignore my {\i1}selamat pagi{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope some upperclassman doesn't call me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, just tell them you're\Na 3rd year student or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not gonna solve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Was that thunder? But it's clear out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might start pouring from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if we get rained on? Or it hails?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining wooden dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right, Yuuko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wooden doll, of all things...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird. I wonder where it came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotta be super rare to be hit\Nby a wooden doll from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It never happens to people, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So maybe I'm extremely lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take that back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A red cow, of all things...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A red cow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's not that I'm lucky.\NThink about it like this, Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least I wasn't hit by anything raw.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like they say, it could've been worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salmon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Tokisadame Prefectural High School" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Come and join the Go+Soccer club!!!" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Selamat pagi{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you reading, Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A real estate magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you moving, Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet again, my {\i1}selamat pagi {\i0}gets no reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well. I think it's time\Nto put that phrase to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Selamat malam{\i0}. [Good Evening]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly Mai! It's {\i1}selamat pagi{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What language is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's time to start homeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... When I got to school this morning,\NI found this in my shoe rack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did any of you put it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anyone who knows\Nwho did it, please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mio. I wonder who could've done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably just a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if it's from some student\Nwho has a crush on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would give their crush a Buddha statue?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I get the feeling of wanting\Nto give something to the person you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I bet you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you feel\Nwhen you think of Sasahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the world am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get home...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakase is probably worried,\Nand it's dangerous to keep the grill burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even get down from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My chopsticks are gone! My slipper, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hand's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will know I'm a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Wonderful" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and eat. Fifth period is our language lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Do you not like sausage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know to save\Nthe best part of your lunch for last?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, you can say "Yum!"\Nwhen you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without further ado... It's chow time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"My Ordinary Life 2" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It broke through!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, Mio! No one ever told\Nyou about the three-second rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so out it's not even funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko's such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First comes rock, then your hand delivers...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it gonna be, no cheats!\NRock-paper-scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the coming of spring,\Nwe welcome a new school year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the days will continue\Nto stay cold for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though in my case, I'll feel\Nthe cold a bit more than all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"My Ordinary Life 3" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please be careful not to catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is my appeal to you as your principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you don't listen and do as I ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:12:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll become the principal\Nof a different school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio, Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? We'll get in trouble if we talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the principal knows\Nthat his jokes aren't funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd think the one saying the jokes\Nwould realize that nobody's laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I don't know, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if he knows he's not funny,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's just trying to teach our\Nlazy generation the importance of persistence?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's actually true,\Nour principal might be a mastermind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's laughing at these terrible jokes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen her laugh this hard in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my one chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:12:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I try saying it now,\NI feel like I'll lose everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say anything until she notices...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just leave it where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Squid tentacle" {\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is a message from\Nthe student counselor, Ms. Sakurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you please, Ms. Sakurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Ms. Sakurai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'm the student counselor, Ms. Sakurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:14:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh... I'm so nervous being\Nin front of this many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I can't let this stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never become\Nthe perfect teacher at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to say what needs to be said!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, I've noticed goats\Nin the school grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please try not to bring goats to the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goats...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with goats?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nowhere in the school policy does it say\Nthat we can't ride a goat to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio? Wasn't that Sasahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Goats can be an exception!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Denied, I say! Denied!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Totally denied!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not allowed to ride goats to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you say, Misato Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I be forced\Nto hobble my way to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the eldest son of the Sasahara household--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that Sasahara household crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are just your typical farmers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what of it? That doesn't change\Nthe fact that I'm the eldest son.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? So Sasahara's family are farmers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel kinda lied to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That white goat at the bike rack\Nmust have been Sasahara's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ban Overruled"\NThat white goat at the bike rack\Nmust have been Sasahara's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Riding majestically atop a white goat,\NSasahara comes to take me away...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A happy new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:16:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Using phones while\Nriding bikes can be very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all stop doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And lastly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning, I found\Na Buddha statue in my shoe rack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not appreciate pranks of this nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. Coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Buddha statue...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai! Don't just stop out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's déjà vu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of you did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be angry,\Nso raise your hand if you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning assembly will not end\Nuntil someone comes forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just say you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I overheard that it was\Nyour birthday, Ms. Sakurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess a Buddha statue\Nwasn't the greatest idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One thought it good for a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Buddha statue gift is not so pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That concludes the morning assembly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will all miss you dearly, Principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Principal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8} "Fire alarm." "Push."{\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Button" "Fire alarm." "Push."{\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't seeing this fire alarm\Nbutton make you wanna push it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you push it? When I pressed it\Nbefore, nothing happened at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do? Run?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, hurry! Out to the yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Quit pushing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pushed me first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You kidding?! You're really ticking me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it! People could die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get outta here! You guys can fight later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helvetica Standard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me? What does "insensitive" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean to be insensitive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me? Please explain\Nbeing insensitive to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me what's insensitive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rules and Essentials"\NKoujirou Sasahara of Class 2-P.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rules and Essentials"\NCome to the faculty room immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True, it may not be against\Nthe school policy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But riding a goat, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't put an end to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:19:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can always ride a bike. Just not a goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tomioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget the Mr.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you not call him a goat,\Nbut Kojiro Sasahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stick with goat for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shinonome Lab"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My Ordinary Life 4"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My Ordinary Life 4"\NMy name is Nano Shinonome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a robot that lives with\NHakase who made me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakase always stays inside the house\Ndoing some sort of research.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm passing the days helping her all that I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakase! I brought some warm milk for y--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really have any special features,\Nbut I apparently have nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nano? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:20:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakase! My pinky toe! My pinky toe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-Pinky t-t-toe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should feel a little better now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really have any special features,\Nbut apparently my pinky toe comes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakase? What is this key for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never wound it up for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but it does spin sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you twist it like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it back. I have\Nall sorts of special features.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? It's cool isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the only reason\Nfor the key on my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:20:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the only reason\Nfor the key on my back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:20:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real, take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's so cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to be more normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit in a chair like normal people...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be able to roll over in bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I'll never be able to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would have been better if you\Nnever made me a humanoid robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nano...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm just kidding, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kidding! You can stop crying now, Hakase!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the Akutagawa Prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akutagawa Prize! Akutagawa Prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my daily life...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wake in the morning, teeth get a brushing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before you know it, it's ten at night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.87,0:22:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Another day was full of laughter{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Another day filled with joy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.17,0:22:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Goofing with friends and acting so silly{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Making a ruckus and then I see{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A glimpse from you and then our eyes meet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.43,0:22:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Coincidence, or not?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.14,0:22:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't ever admit it's first love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.69,0:22:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's not something I would say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.73,0:22:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, I'll see you again tomorrow too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I close my eyes I see {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.99,0:22:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My vision sparkling, filled with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.12,0:22:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wasn't it so much fun today?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.45,0:23:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, I think I'm in love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so happy I'm so happy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nice to meet you, awakening love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.97,0:23:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll see you again tomorrow too{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.10,0:23:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll see you again soon in my dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! I'm Nano's big toe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My capacity is one gigabyte.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you wish I had more storage?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.54,0:23:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The next {\i1}My Ordinary Life {\i0}is Episode 2!{\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.50,0:23:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Narration: Reiko Katsura"\NThe next {\i1}My Ordinary Life {\i0}is Episode 2!{\an}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Narration: Reiko Katsura"\NLook forward to it!{\an}